item.title: Biography
item.description: Zeke Taylor (born December 29, 2005) is an American actor and internet personality. He is best known for his roles in Merman Academy (2015), NicheZeke (2013),Theories With Zeke (2019), Lucid Nonsense (2020) and The Witches (2020).

item.title: Filmography
item.description: Ever since his career started. Zeke has been in several television and film works in the entertainment industry, [mainly televison though]. And almost all of them have been his creations and projects. This page is a full overview of the filmography of Zeke Taylor.
